Type of Feat: Class
Prerequisite: Dragon Disciple level 3.
Specifics: At 3rd level, the dragon disciple gains the ability to breate a cone of their dragon's element that deals 2d10 points of damage to all creatures within its area. This damage increases to 4d10 at 7th level and 6d10 at 10th level. Targets may make a Reflex save (DC 10 + 1/2 the red dragon disciple's class level + the disciple's Charisma bonus).
Use: Selected. This ability may be used once per day.
Black, Green, and Copper dragon disciples deal Acid damage. Blue and Bronze dragon disciples deal Lightning damage. White and Silver dragon disciples deal Cold damage. Red, Brass, and Gold dragon disciples deal Fire damage.